name: Seas of Europa - Still Frame
description: Seas of Europa is an animated artwork I've been working on for quite some time. The animated version is still not completely finished, the overall appearance of the work is at the point where I feel that a still frame from the animation is worth publishing. The general idea of this artwork is to imagine, using half a dozen or so Artbreeder generated creatures, how the seas of Europa might be populated.
